Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著大家再次降生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這裡等著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在流逝的時光中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一刻緊接一刻地死亡  一刻緊接一刻地轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從無到有的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:52.55,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:59.75,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:15.40,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:25.87,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:37.95,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:48.54,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.70,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:02:00.55,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:04.92,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.26,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.27,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:52.55,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:59.75,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:15.40,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:25.87,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:37.95,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:48.54,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.70,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:02:00.55,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:04.92,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.26,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.27,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===============OP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,390)\fs32\fad(600,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1B1B1B&\be5\blur2}愛的野獸們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 盡是些淡而無味的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那傢伙會在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前那野獸一般的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不經誕生禮節儀式之人不會有真正的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於自黑暗深淵中重生的他們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正好是恰當的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓女人全部退後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的目標是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得這是性別歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是說這話的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對手是血肉之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想一下白刃戰的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我的洞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是墓穴特訓的成果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空間填補
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配合得如此默契
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心有靈犀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫唱婦隨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆轉之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將填埋的力量轉換成了開辟的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢對我耍花招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 你要對Mix做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 這傢伙也是香氣撲鼻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 他只對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來保護御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸井
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不要妨礙我和臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋居然叫御子乃做臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然連傷害都可以逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直率地朝向想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個聲音…又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡做些奇怪的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在奏響大地與空氣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你那逆轉的不諧和音已經耳熟能詳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能被你妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人是只屬於…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只屬於我一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一舉逆轉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野獸的猛攻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是一種有趣的音色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說他看上了御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人對一個女人窮追不舍的理由只有這一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 男人追男人也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據諸井發來的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以判斷那傢伙現正挾持著御子乃潛伏在市內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就在地面進行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兵分兩路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到那邊去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 我也跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 我只是要殺了你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你死在我的臂彎裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影 你聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經把氣味的源頭弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快讓我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是使用方式有誤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影你睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊已經完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽得很清楚啊 愛的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}未影 快讓我回來 未影 快回話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微讓我捉弄一下有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰不會妒忌搶先得到心頭好的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃肯定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道? 知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他絕對不會加害於御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼那麼肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 他是御子乃命中注定的對像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃的真命天子不是阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聞到了 果然很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼你總是說出這麼過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 我和你明明無怨無仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你一直待在Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣 現在你在這裡把我殺掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我 在這種地方也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要我住手 那我就住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這根本就沒住手嘛 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想讓我舔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想…想殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是反語?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只對你說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…這雙眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺好令人懷念…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲 和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前也這麼叫過我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲和阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神話說的就是我們的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創世之初
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生命之樹下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偉大的生命之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌管著該星球所有的生靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也掌管著星球自身的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在兩個種族的紛爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽之翼覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且給生命之樹授粉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 生命之樹的花朵卻沒有結出果實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那麼漸漸枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這星球將變成永無生命誕生的荒蕪之地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心相愛的阿波隆和希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護生命之樹而天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是希爾菲說道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會一直等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要等一萬兩千年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一萬兩千年之後再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…阿波隆的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是…阿波隆?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想說御子乃就是希爾菲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會想出那麼荒謬的事情來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我無意中看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也就能跟怪炎那喪服的婚禮的影像銜接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔也看過那影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波隆什麼的 希爾菲什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是個傳說而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當真能夠如此斷定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我稍微有點高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如果御子乃和那傢伙真的是被命運所繫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定…阿馬塔和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡 你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝴蝶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼晚了還在出沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…我不是什麼希爾菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是…什麼希爾菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嚇我 希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糾纏不休的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有種能夠成功的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧特訓的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經能把那傢伙的力量稍微抵銷一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所願 他沖著我這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來把將傢伙從御子乃身邊引開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趕快聯絡怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他這樣不就成英雄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 是御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎說他馬上就過來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔你快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在御子乃成功逃脫之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得拖延住那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我去…死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死你 我要殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屢次三番地…殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要死了嗎 我…要死在這裡嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要陷入那黑暗的深淵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那黑暗之中…我又要變得孤身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔·空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗再也不是你為情所困而飽受煎熬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是為了斬斷如今的執著 締結新的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 把自己束縛在黑暗和孤獨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨棄過去和執著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糾纏不休的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆向飛翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 我的力量會不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無執著的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不為一切外物所惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子是趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 不要掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我收拾掉他之前你就待在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 快給他最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是身處在以命相搏的立場上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要開槍 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒這個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如象徵著復活的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不被允許的愛啊 儘管蘇醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越一萬兩千年的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------ED------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:58.44,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:06.25,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:16.23,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:25.73,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:33.59,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:41.18,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:45.37,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:48.53,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:53.06,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:56.27,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:00.60,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:07.11,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:58.44,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 點綴著雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:06.25,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}從睡夢中驚醒之後 遠望著憂傷的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:16.23,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這份青澀的感覺 依存在綠葉錯綜的紋路之間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:25.73,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}側耳聆聽 晨露緩緩落下的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:33.59,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所創造的這個世界並不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:41.18,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因為這裡每天都有戀情一段接一段地告終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:45.37,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初嘗戀愛的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:48.53,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這個你應該不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:53.06,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不見天日也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:56.27,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:00.60,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘卻也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:07.11,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------ED------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我興奮並如此發酵的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一萬兩千年的命運的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.03,0:24:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也委身於這臭氣吧 希爾菲
